<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="A" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Axe" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Axe,</orth> instrument to hew timber, to chop wood, or to kill cattle: <cit><quote>a butcher with an a.</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h6 3.2.189" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B III, 2, 189</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>many strokes, though with a little a., hew down the oak,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 3h6 2.1.54" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C II, 1, 54</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 2.2.165" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 2, 165</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 5.2.11" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 2, 11</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tit 3.1.185" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. III, 1, 185</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tit 3.1.185" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. III, 1, 185</bibl> <bibl n="shak. tim 5.1.214" default="NO" valid="yes">Tim. V, 1, 214</bibl>. Metaphorically: <cit><quote>is hacked down and his summer leaves all faded by murder's bloody a.</quote> <bibl n="shak. r2 1.2.21" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 I, 2, 21</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>hew my way out with a bloody a.</quote> <bibl n="shak. 3h6 3.2.181" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C III, 2, 181</bibl></cit>.<lb />Especially the executioner's axe: <bibl n="shak. mm 4.2.56" default="NO" valid="yes">Meas. IV, 2, 56</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mm 4.3.39" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 3, 39</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mv 4.1.125" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. IV, 1, 125</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ayl 3.5.5" default="NO" valid="yes">As III, 5, 5</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 2.4.49" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B II, 4, 49</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h8 2.1.61" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 II, 1, 61</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h8 3.2.264" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 2, 264</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. rom 3.3.22" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. III, 3, 22</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 4.5.218" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. IV, 5, 218</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 5.2.24" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 2, 24</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. per 1.2.58" default="NO" valid="yes">Per. I, 2, 58</bibl>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>